Put it on your glasses.
Put it on your glasses.

20:50.771 --> 20:54.470
Okay, just mailed in my last
recco and application.

20:54.514 --> 20:56.342
Only a few months left,
and I'm outta this dump.

20:56.385 --> 20:58.213
School sucks.
I'll cherish you all.

20:58.257 --> 21:01.434
Our lives
are finally beginning, JTP.

21:01.477 --> 21:04.393
I can't wait to come back
for our 10-year reunion

21:04.437 --> 21:06.526
and show everyone
how awesome we all are.

21:06.569 --> 21:08.310
Oh, we'll show 'em
when I roll up with Erica,

21:08.354 --> 21:10.225
and I'll be like, "'Sup!
This wasn't a fluke."

21:10.269 --> 21:12.619
Well, I'll cruise in
on my rocket boots

21:12.662 --> 21:15.665
and my two wives
named Heather...
Locklear and Thomas.

21:15.709 --> 21:18.973
Oh, yeah?
I'm gonna beam here
from planet Barry,

21:19.016 --> 21:22.759
where I ride space elephants
and rule Rap City
with an iron fist.

21:22.803 --> 21:24.587
Wow, I can't wait
for this reunion.

21:24.631 --> 21:26.459
Reunions!
JTP: Reunions!
